    <title>Alternate Authentication Endpoints</title>
    <para> 
        You can use the current Cloud Identity authentication endpoints with earlier versions of the API. 
        All versions of the API, including legacy Identity contracts, are available if you authenticate 
        at a current endpoint and specify an API version. 
    </para>
    <important>
        <para>
            You can use either UK or US endpoints, regardless of where your account was created.
        </para>
    </important>
    <para> Rackspace recommends that you authenticate at one of the following Cloud Identity endpoints: </para>
